I19(e) Deposit of moneys in general fund; reimbursement of United States for administration of chapter

I11Moneys received from application fees established under this section shall be deposited in the general fund of the Treasury to reimburse the United States for amounts appropriated for use by the Commission in carrying out its functions under this chapter.

I19(f) Rules and regulations

I11The Commission shall prescribe appropriate rules and regulations to carry out the provisions of this section.

