I14(iii) unauthorized access, including so-called ``hacking'', and other unlawful activities by minors online;

I14(iv) unauthorized disclosure, use, and dissemination of personal identification information regarding minors; and

I14(v) measures designed to restrict minors' access to materials harmful to minors; and

