I79(3) Video programming services; other programming services

I12The terms ``video programming service'' and ``other programming services'' have the same meanings as such terms have under section 522 of this title.

I19(j) Certain service applications treated as in-region service applications

I11For purposes of this section, a Bell operating company application to provide 800 service, private line service, or their equivalents that_

I12(1) terminate in an in-region State of that Bell operating company, and

I12(2) allow the called party to determine the interLATA carrier,

