I12(D) has transmitted superfluous radio communications or signals or communications containing profane or obscene words, language, or meaning, or has knowingly transmitted_

I13(1) false or deceptive signals or communications, or

I13(2) a call signal or letter which has not been assigned by proper authority to the station he is operating; or

