I12(2) the expansion of the service areas of existing public telecommunications entities;

I12(3) the development of public telecommunications facilities owned by, operated by, and available to minorities and women; and

I12(4) the improvement of the capabilities of existing public broadcast stations to provide public telecommunications services, including services to underserved audiences such as deaf and hearing impaired individuals and blind and visually impaired individuals.

I19(c) Noncommercial radio broadcast station facilities

I11Of the sums appropriated pursuant to section 391 of this title for any fiscal year, a substantial amount shall be available for the expansion and development of noncommercial radio broadcast station facilities.

