I12(17) the term ``service tier'' means a category of cable service or other services provided by a cable operator and for which a separate rate is charged by the cable operator;

I12(18) the term ``State'' means any State, or political subdivision, or agency thereof;

I12(19) the term ``usable activated channels'' means activated channels of a cable system, except those channels whose use for the distribution of broadcast signals would conflict with technical and safety regulations as determined by the Commission; and

