I89. Identification of reallocable frequencies

I19(a) Identification required

I11The Secretary shall, within 18 months after August 10, 1993, and within 6 months after August 5, 1997, prepare and submit to the President and the Congress a report identifying and recommending for reallocation bands of frequencies_

I12(1) that are allocated on a primary basis for Federal Government use;

I12(2) that are not required for the present or identifiable future needs of the Federal Government;

