I19(g) Restriction on use of Funds

I11No amounts in the Fund on the day before February 22, 2012, may be used for any purpose except_

I12(1) to pay the relocation or sharing costs incurred by eligible Federal entities in order to relocate from the frequencies the auction of which generated such amounts; or

I12(2) to pay relocation or sharing costs related to pre-auction estimates or research, in accordance with subsection (d)(3).

